Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.77,0:00:04.05,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,One, two, three, four!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.05,0:00:07.08,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,One, two, three, four!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.94,0:00:11.33,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,It's about time for a break, Katsuragi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.33,0:00:13.98,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Oh, okay...!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.98,0:00:15.25,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.63,0:00:20.90,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Lately, you've been listening to what I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.90,0:00:23.78,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Oh, come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.78,0:00:28.20,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,You're making me sound like a spoiled brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.20,0:00:31.73,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,There are people who won't do something unless they're told to, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.73,0:00:34.90,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,I've never seen someone who won't take a break unless they're told to.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.90,0:00:38.64,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Uh, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.64,0:00:42.36,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,In fact, there are times when I tell you to rest, and you still don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.36,0:00:44.87,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Hahaha...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.87,0:00:48.47,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Don't try to laugh it off. Honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.47,0:00:51.74,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,But more importantly, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.74,0:00:55.09,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,What's our next goal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.09,0:00:58.94,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Well, if we're setting the next goal, it would probably be 'H.I.F.', but—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.94,0:01:02.05,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Given the current situation, it's unlikely we'll qualify.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.05,0:01:05.58,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.58,0:01:08.87,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,However, there is a solid foundation for you to soar, Katsuragi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.87,0:01:11.27,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,A foundation...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.27,0:01:14.99,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,An event for the next generation of idols... It's perfect for you, Katsuragi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.99,0:01:19.76,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Wow, that sounds incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.76,0:01:24.02,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I definitely want to participate, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.02,0:01:28.06,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'll spread my wings there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.32,0:01:44.02,Default,黒井崇男,0,0,0,,The time has finally come.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.02,0:01:49.88,Default,黒井崇男,0,0,0,,The time has come for our Gokugetsu Academy to crush Hatsuboshi Academy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.88,0:01:54.50,Default,黒井崇男,0,0,0,,Shion, you understand why you've been called here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.50,0:02:01.37,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,So I just need to massacre the students of Hatsuboshi Academy, is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.37,0:02:04.07,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,...Should we call on Gekka-neesama?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.07,0:02:08.50,Default,黒井崇男,0,0,0,,No, as long as a Prima Stella doesn't show up,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.50,0:02:10.93,Default,黒井崇男,0,0,0,,There's no need to call Gekka back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.93,0:02:13.05,Default,黒井崇男,0,0,0,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.05,0:02:16.69,Default,黒井崇男,0,0,0,,I've already put a plan in place to crush them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.69,0:02:18.80,Default,黒井崇男,0,0,0,,Shion.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.80,0:02:26.27,Default,黒井崇男,0,0,0,,We'll show those incompetents the true power of Gokugetsu Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.27,0:02:27.56,Default,黒井崇男,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.56,0:02:30.37,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,Understood, Chairman.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.37,0:02:37.55,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,I'll take care of those foolish Hatsuboshi students myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.49,0:02:41.58,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,"The Next Idol Audition..."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.58,0:02:45.63,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,That's my next goal, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.63,0:02:49.37,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,That's right, Katsuragi-san. To achieve that goal, you need to――
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.37,0:02:53.36,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I need to grow my fanbase...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.36,0:02:54.47,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,That's right, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.47,0:02:56.39,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,That's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.39,0:02:59.16,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,My fans...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.16,0:03:02.20,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I just can't picture it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.20,0:03:08.26,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'm sure there will be lots of amazing idols competing, right...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.26,0:03:14.36,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Will there be anyone cheering for me among them...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.36,0:03:18.17,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,At the very least, there's one person right in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.96,0:03:21.85,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.85,0:03:24.21,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.21,0:03:26.86,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I've gained a little bit of courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.86,0:03:29.83,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,'N.I.A.' is a nationwide competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.83,0:03:34.05,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Katsuragi-san, you're going to be in the spotlight more than ever before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.05,0:03:37.27,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.27,0:03:38.70,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'm nervous...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.70,0:03:42.64,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Thanks to your lessons, you're able to sing in front of an audience, Katsuragi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.64,0:03:46.76,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,That said, overcoming something you're not good at isn't so easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.76,0:03:49.55,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Y-yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.55,0:03:53.47,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Just imagining it makes my stomach hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.47,0:03:58.09,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Let's take it step by step. This competition is the perfect opportunity for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.09,0:04:00.94,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'll do my best...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.94,0:04:06.43,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...But what should I do to win over the fans?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.43,0:04:10.70,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,We have various activities planned, but I'll handle the scheduling.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.70,0:04:14.42,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,As always, just keep giving it your all, Katsuragi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.42,0:04:18.14,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Is that really enough...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.14,0:04:20.83,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Yes. I'm sure that's the best way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.83,0:04:24.08,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Well, I'm not really sure, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.08,0:04:27.55,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I trust your words, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.55,0:04:31.27,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'm really good at giving it my all...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.27,0:04:34.49,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...That's all I can do, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.49,0:04:37.79,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,It's okay. You're definitely growing, Katsuragi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.81,0:04:41.67,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Step by step, steadily. Now you can hold your own against other idols.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.67,0:04:44.89,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.89,0:04:47.80,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Hehe... I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.80,0:04:49.84,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,You have a great expression, Katsuragi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.84,0:04:50.91,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Eek...!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.91,0:04:52.69,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,S-Senpai...!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.69,0:04:57.31,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Can I post this photo on social media? I want people to get to know you, Katsuragi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.31,0:05:01.25,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I don't mind, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.25,0:05:04.25,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,You didn't have to take it so suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.25,0:05:06.87,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,So, is it okay if I take the photo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.87,0:05:10.86,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Oh, this is so embarrassing...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.86,0:05:13.91,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.91,0:05:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,If it means gaining more fans...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.45,0:05:19.70,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,That's the spirit. Gaining fans is the first step to becoming an idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.70,0:05:23.51,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,I'll do my best to help share your charm with as many people as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.51,0:05:25.43,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Thank you... I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.43,0:05:27.71,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Let's rise to the top together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.71,0:05:28.98,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Yes...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.90,0:05:34.82,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Look, Katsuragi-san. The number of votes has increased since yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.82,0:05:37.82,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Really...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.82,0:05:40.86,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I can hardly believe it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.86,0:05:46.16,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I wonder why they became my fans...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.16,0:05:49.80,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,There are a lot of different opinions out there. But the most common one is—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.80,0:05:52.69,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Seeing you work so hard is really inspiring.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.92,0:05:57.39,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,I feel the same way. I always feel better watching you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.39,0:06:00.61,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Hehe... I'm so happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.61,0:06:04.08,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,(...The number of votes for Katsuragi-san are gradually increasing.)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.08,0:06:08.15,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,(However, it's true that the number is still lower compared to other idols.)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.10,0:06:12.20,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Senpai...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.20,0:06:13.96,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.96,0:06:16.18,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,...No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.18,0:06:20.15,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,(For now, I'll keep quiet. What Katsuragi-san needs is confidence.)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.82,0:06:27.50,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Can I take a guess at what you're thinking, Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.50,0:06:29.31,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.31,0:06:32.31,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,If you're talking about the vote counts for other idols,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.31,0:06:34.69,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,You can tell just by looking at the rankings.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.69,0:06:38.98,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Of course, I know that my position is low.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.98,0:06:40.90,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.90,0:06:44.27,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Even so, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.27,0:06:48.29,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'm more happy than frustrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.29,0:06:52.60,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,It might be fewer compared to other idols, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.60,0:06:54.70,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Even so,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.70,0:07:00.38,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,So many people have come to like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.38,0:07:04.42,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,They wanted to support someone like me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.42,0:07:06.61,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,That's what they thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.61,0:07:08.33,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.33,0:07:11.20,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'm really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.20,0:07:14.85,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,For you, Katsuragi-san, fans aren't just numbers, are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.85,0:07:17.31,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...They aren't, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.31,0:07:20.39,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Each and every one of them is important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.39,0:07:27.21,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Well, of course, having more fans would be great.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.21,0:07:30.97,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,(...As a professional, I tend to focus on numbers, but I really need to reflect on that.)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.97,0:07:34.80,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Katsuragi-san, you're doing great just as you are. Let's keep moving forward with your activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.80,0:07:36.20,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Yes...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.49,0:07:43.20,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,We're performing at an event today. We were lucky that a spot opened up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.20,0:07:46.85,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Wow, there are so many people here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.85,0:07:50.89,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,This time, a lot of top idols from 'N.I.A' will be performing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.89,0:07:54.16,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,There are so many famous people here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.16,0:07:58.98,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Is it really okay for me to be here...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.98,0:08:03.20,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,It's true that the other performers are all top-tier idols compared to you, Katsuragi-san, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.20,0:08:07.17,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,It's an opportunity for many people to get to know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.17,0:08:09.86,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I-I understand...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.86,0:08:13.54,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Do your best. I'm cheering for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.05,0:08:19.02,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I completely messed up...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.02,0:08:23.22,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I wonder if Senpai is disappointed in me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.22,0:08:25.84,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,Hey, you over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.84,0:08:26.99,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.99,0:08:29.96,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,May I ask for your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.96,0:08:33.33,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'm... Lilja Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.33,0:08:35.09,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,...Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.09,0:08:37.12,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,I've never heard of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.12,0:08:39.62,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,The number of followers is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.62,0:08:41.32,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.32,0:08:42.74,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,Isn't it too few?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.49,0:08:48.08,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,...I'm genuinely curious, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.08,0:08:50.91,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,Why are you even here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.91,0:08:53.60,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'm... I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.60,0:08:59.21,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,You should know your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.21,0:09:02.80,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,You were holding us back today, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.80,0:09:04.68,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,Are you even aware of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.68,0:09:07.60,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.60,0:09:09.00,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.00,0:09:14.99,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,...Even after all that, you can't muster a single complaint, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.99,0:09:17.95,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...I was the one holding everyone back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.95,0:09:19.41,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,That's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.41,0:09:22.28,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,So... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.28,0:09:27.17,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'll make sure it doesn't happen again next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.87,0:09:33.04,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,This is just some friendly advice—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.04,0:09:37.45,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,You don't have any talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.45,0:09:40.33,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,I suggest you quit while you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.33,0:09:44.10,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I know that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.10,0:09:48.08,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Even so, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.08,0:09:51.22,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I've decided to become an idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.22,0:09:54.24,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,...I don't like that look in your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.24,0:09:57.05,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,Oh, by the way—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.05,0:10:02.34,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,So, you have a producer backing you too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.34,0:10:05.34,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.34,0:10:07.69,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,He's a really kind person.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.69,0:10:10.46,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,He really doesn't have an eye for talent, does he?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.46,0:10:15.08,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,Just like you—no talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.08,0:10:16.73,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.73,0:10:19.73,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,And he doesn't even notice it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.73,0:10:23.29,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,Maybe he's not that bright too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.29,0:10:25.04,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.55,0:10:29.68,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...Take that back, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.68,0:10:33.13,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I can't forgive you for badmouthing Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.13,0:10:34.48,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.48,0:10:37.34,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,I was just stating the facts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.34,0:10:39.71,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,Do you really have a reason to be angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.71,0:10:42.33,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.33,0:10:45.15,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,So... please take it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.15,0:10:47.73,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,Heh heh heh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.73,0:10:50.45,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,Are you frustrated?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.45,0:10:53.44,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,Well, this is pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.44,0:10:56.44,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,There's a world of difference between your level and mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.44,0:10:58.36,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,Know your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.04,0:11:03.38,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,Well then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.84,0:11:11.37,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,(...I couldn't say anything.)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.37,0:11:14.35,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,(It doesn't matter what I say right now.)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.35,0:11:18.16,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,(I can't prove it.)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.16,0:11:21.90,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,(Because I don't have any talent...)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.90,0:11:25.54,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,(I thought it didn't matter what anyone said.)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.54,0:11:27.99,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,(But...)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.99,0:11:32.68,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,(I can't stand it when Senpai is insulted because of me...)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.68,0:11:34.71,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,(Unforgivable)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.71,0:11:36.41,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,If that's the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.41,0:11:41.78,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I can't stay like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.87,0:11:51.10,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,No... no, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.10,0:11:54.48,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Sharper, smoother...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.48,0:11:56.37,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,...Katsuragi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.37,0:11:58.72,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.72,0:12:00.00,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.00,0:12:02.31,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Is there something on your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.31,0:12:04.78,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...No, not really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.78,0:12:07.68,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,There's really nothing in particular...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.68,0:12:10.66,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,If you say so. I just hope that's really the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.79,0:12:14.42,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.42,0:12:16.35,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'll continue with the lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.35,0:12:20.16,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,You seem out of breath. How about we take a little break?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.16,0:12:22.11,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.11,0:12:24.05,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'm fine...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.05,0:12:26.28,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I can still keep going!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.28,0:12:28.68,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Please don't push yourself too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.68,0:12:30.90,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'm almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.90,0:12:35.27,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I feel like I'm on the verge of something...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.27,0:12:39.91,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,(What is this feeling...? It's not just about being motivated...)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.91,0:12:42.60,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,(It's like there's an intense, almost overwhelming energy...)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.60,0:12:44.50,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.50,0:12:46.38,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.38,0:12:48.69,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I was mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.69,0:12:50.80,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Mistaken...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.80,0:12:52.79,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Until now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.79,0:12:56.08,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Even if I lost to other idols,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.08,0:12:59.63,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Somewhere in my heart, I always thought this:
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.63,0:13:02.53,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,"It can't be helped."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.53,0:13:05.99,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Everyone else is more amazing than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.29,0:13:11.81,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,But that's not how it should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.81,0:13:14.77,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,With that kind of mindset...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.77,0:13:16.73,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,There's no way I can win 'N.I.A.'
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.73,0:13:19.18,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,...You're right about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.18,0:13:21.47,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.47,0:13:24.20,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I will win.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.20,0:13:28.32,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'll definitely pass the next audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.32,0:13:31.44,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,...Yes, that's the spirit. I'm rooting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.44,0:13:33.28,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.28,0:13:35.60,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,(Something definitely happened.)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.67,0:13:43.15,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...Yeah, just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.15,0:13:45.98,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,There weren't any major mistakes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.98,0:13:47.52,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.52,0:13:50.61,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Let's check the choreography and go through it one more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.61,0:13:52.90,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,That's enough, Katsuragi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.90,0:13:55.18,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Huh, Senpai...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.18,0:13:58.17,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Why are you here...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.17,0:14:02.26,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,That's my line. Didn't I tell you we're done for today?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.26,0:14:05.91,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,But... just a little longer...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.91,0:14:09.15,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Katsuragi-san, I've told you before. Overworking yourself isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.15,0:14:13.22,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,What's going on? Katsuragi-san seems to be in a rush about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.22,0:14:15.22,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.97,0:14:20.19,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I don't want to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.19,0:14:22.06,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,...Katsuragi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.06,0:14:24.27,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.27,0:14:26.90,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.90,0:14:30.86,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,(It seems like she'll continue practicing when no one's watching.)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.86,0:14:33.91,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,(No matter what happened, she's in a precarious state right now.)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.56,0:14:37.93,Default,紫雲清夏,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.93,0:14:40.66,Default,紫雲清夏,0,0,0,,Did you come to ask me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.66,0:14:44.52,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Yes, I thought you might know something, Shiun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.52,0:14:50.32,Default,紫雲清夏,0,0,0,,...Sorry, I want to help, but I don't know either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.32,0:14:54.86,Default,紫雲清夏,0,0,0,,Of course, I've noticed that Lilja's been acting a bit strange lately, but....
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.86,0:14:59.00,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,I told her to take a break today, but do you know where Katsuragi-san is?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.00,0:15:03.25,Default,紫雲清夏,0,0,0,,Probably practicing somewhere, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.25,0:15:06.01,Default,紫雲清夏,0,0,0,,And probably making sure no one knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.01,0:15:09.06,Default,紫雲清夏,0,0,0,,...the movie of Lilja's favorite anime just came out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.06,0:15:11.51,Default,紫雲清夏,0,0,0,,It was just released yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.51,0:15:14.17,Default,紫雲清夏,0,0,0,,I invited her, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.17,0:15:16.08,Default,紫雲清夏,0,0,0,,She turned me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.08,0:15:22.69,Default,紫雲清夏,0,0,0,,She's not willing to talk to either you or me, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.69,0:15:24.39,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Shiun-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.39,0:15:28.16,Default,紫雲清夏,0,0,0,,I couldn't stop her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.16,0:15:31.53,Default,紫雲清夏,0,0,0,,...Please, Producer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.53,0:15:33.38,Default,紫雲清夏,0,0,0,,Please stop Lilja.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.38,0:15:35.85,Default,紫雲清夏,0,0,0,,The way she is now...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.85,0:15:38.85,Default,紫雲清夏,0,0,0,,It's scary to watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.85,0:15:42.91,Default,紫雲清夏,0,0,0,,She reminds me a lot of how I was before I got injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.84,0:15:46.43,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,(Today's a day off...)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.43,0:15:50.23,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,(But I can't afford to take a break right now.)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.23,0:15:53.03,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,(I, who lacks talent,)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.03,0:15:56.02,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,(To surpass the other idols—)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.02,0:16:01.49,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,(I have to push myself harder than them.)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.78,0:16:06.57,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Katsuragi-san, I've told you before. Overworking yourself isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.72,0:16:12.27,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,(If it means proving myself—)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.27,0:16:16.84,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,(I don't care if my body breaks down)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.84,0:16:19.33,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,(...I'm sorry, Senpai)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.33,0:16:22.52,Default,紫雲清夏,0,0,0,,...Lilja?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.52,0:16:26.12,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Oh, good morning, Sumika-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.12,0:16:31.61,Default,紫雲清夏,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.61,0:16:35.08,Default,紫雲清夏,0,0,0,,Where are you going so early in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.08,0:16:39.20,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...I'm just going for a little walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.20,0:16:43.57,Default,紫雲清夏,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.57,0:16:46.32,Default,紫雲清夏,0,0,0,,Have a good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.32,0:16:50.98,Default,紫雲清夏,0,0,0,,I'm still sleepy, so I'm going to sleep a little longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.98,0:16:54.35,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Alright, I'm heading out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.35,0:17:00.69,Default,紫雲清夏,0,0,0,,...So sleepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.69,0:17:02.75,Default,紫雲清夏,0,0,0,,...Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.75,0:17:05.59,Default,紫雲清夏,0,0,0,,Wait, hold on, is she going for a walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.59,0:17:11.11,Default,紫雲清夏,0,0,0,,Wasn't today supposed to be her complete rest day...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.11,0:17:12.92,Default,紫雲清夏,0,0,0,,No way...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.37,0:17:23.14,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.14,0:17:25.28,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,My throat...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.28,0:17:27.69,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,(Something's wrong...)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.69,0:17:30.79,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,(My vision is getting blurry.)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.79,0:17:34.77,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,(I can't... I need to focus more...)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.78,0:17:43.16,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Shiun-san, how's it going over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.16,0:17:45.42,Default,紫雲清夏,0,0,0,,I'm looking everywhere I can think of, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.42,0:17:47.45,Default,紫雲清夏,0,0,0,,I can't find her anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.45,0:17:50.24,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,In that case, could she be in the practice room...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.47,0:17:54.04,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Katsuragi-san!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.04,0:17:56.71,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Oh, Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.11,0:18:02.30,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,It looks like you've twisted your ankle. I'll call the nurse!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.87,0:18:06.64,Default,保健医,0,0,0,,It looks like you've sprained your ankle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.64,0:18:10.57,Default,保健医,0,0,0,,It doesn't seem like there's any bone damage, but you should rest for a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.57,0:18:13.79,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.79,0:18:17.48,Default,保健医,0,0,0,,Alright, I'll leave you for now. Please make sure to come back to the nurse's office for a follow-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.48,0:18:21.15,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,...Katsuragi-san. I told you today was a rest day, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.15,0:18:23.27,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.27,0:18:26.97,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for not listening to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.97,0:18:30.06,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for being disobedient.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.06,0:18:34.98,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Even so, I just can't help but...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.98,0:18:38.12,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Please tell me what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.12,0:18:40.72,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.72,0:18:44.22,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,This is your punishment for breaking the rules. Please tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.14,0:18:50.50,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,She spoke badly about you, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.50,0:18:52.73,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.73,0:18:57.22,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,She said you don't have an eye for talent, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.22,0:19:01.42,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,She said you don't have talent, just like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.42,0:19:04.15,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,She went that far...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.13,0:19:08.00,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Even after hearing all that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.00,0:19:13.39,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,—I couldn't talk back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.45,0:19:22.34,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,The reason She said that about you was because I'm not skilled enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.36,0:19:28.52,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,If I were a more amazing idol, no one would ever say any thing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.52,0:19:33.42,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,So I need to show her!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.42,0:19:39.05,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,That the idol you found can get real results!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.05,0:19:41.35,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,As long as we can smile in the end, that's all that matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.83,0:19:43.30,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.30,0:19:46.99,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,No matter how much we're ridiculed along the way, it doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.99,0:19:50.17,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...Even though it's my fault...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.17,0:19:53.68,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,I'm the one who made the choice. It's not your fault, Katsuragi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.68,0:19:55.90,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,But, still...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.90,0:19:59.55,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,There are no shortcuts on the path to becoming an idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.55,0:20:02.54,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Pushing yourself too hard won't get you there any faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.54,0:20:04.25,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.25,0:20:08.21,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Overexerting yourself somewhere along the way can actually end up being a detour.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.21,0:20:11.83,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Like now, right...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.83,0:20:15.40,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Your ability to give it your all is one of your greatest strengths, Katsuragi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.40,0:20:19.44,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,But seeing you push yourself too hard like this... it's a bit worrying.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.44,0:20:21.04,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.04,0:20:23.44,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,I'm relieved it's not a serious injury.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.44,0:20:27.39,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,It's disheartening to see my guidance being ignored like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.39,0:20:29.70,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.70,0:20:33.42,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,I believe that you can become a top idol, Katsuragi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.42,0:20:37.42,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,So, Katsuragi-san, I want you to trust your Producer—trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.42,0:20:39.14,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.14,0:20:44.44,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I didn't consider your feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.44,0:20:48.56,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,I'll prove myself to be a producer worthy of a top idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.56,0:20:52.62,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,I'll make sure no one ever says I lack vision or talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.62,0:20:56.74,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,…I believe you, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.74,0:20:58.47,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,And your words.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.47,0:21:01.09,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Let's rise together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.09,0:21:03.66,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,We'll be the ones laughing in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.66,0:21:05.70,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.70,0:21:08.35,Default,紫雲清夏,0,0,0,,Lilja!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.35,0:21:10.20,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Sumika-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.20,0:21:13.14,Default,紫雲清夏,0,0,0,,Oh, your foot... are you okay!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.14,0:21:15.86,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,It's just a sprain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.86,0:21:18.46,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I think it'll heal in about a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.46,0:21:21.43,Default,紫雲清夏,0,0,0,,Oh, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.43,0:21:24.68,Default,紫雲清夏,0,0,0,,I'm so relieved...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.68,0:21:27.30,Default,紫雲清夏,0,0,0,,It's not a serious injury.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.30,0:21:28.97,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.97,0:21:32.48,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.48,0:21:34.55,Default,紫雲清夏,0,0,0,,It's not about being sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.55,0:21:36.96,Default,紫雲清夏,0,0,0,,You're always pushing yourself too hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.96,0:21:39.43,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.43,0:21:42.02,Default,紫雲清夏,0,0,0,,Overworking yourself isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.02,0:21:43.95,Default,紫雲清夏,0,0,0,,Didn't the Producer tell you that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.95,0:21:46.54,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.54,0:21:49.36,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I just got scolded...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.37,0:21:53.61,Default,紫雲清夏,0,0,0,,...Lilja.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.61,0:21:56.49,Default,紫雲清夏,0,0,0,,If this were a serious injury,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.49,0:21:58.87,Default,紫雲清夏,0,0,0,,You wouldn't be able to move for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.87,0:22:01.34,Default,紫雲清夏,0,0,0,,In fact,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.34,0:22:06.93,Default,紫雲清夏,0,0,0,,Your dream... it might not come true, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.93,0:22:10.08,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Sumika-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.08,0:22:14.38,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.38,0:22:18.57,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I... didn't understand anything at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.57,0:22:23.54,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,But it's okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.54,0:22:27.35,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'll stop pushing myself too hard on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.35,0:22:31.70,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Because I trust Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.69,0:22:35.99,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Oh, Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.99,0:22:38.02,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.02,0:22:41.59,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,I came to check if you're really taking a break, Katsuragi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.59,0:22:46.20,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,You don't have to be so suspicious...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.20,0:22:49.37,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'm really just relaxing at the dorm.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.37,0:22:52.57,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,I'm worried... I'm concerned you might be overdoing it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.57,0:22:55.91,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I've learned my lesson...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.91,0:22:58.48,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Oh, hey, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.48,0:23:02.61,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,If you'd like, please have some of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.61,0:23:04.98,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Oh, is this... a cream puff?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.98,0:23:08.65,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Well, I didn't have much else to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.65,0:23:10.82,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I was just making some sweets.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.82,0:23:13.19,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Thank you, I'll gladly enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.19,0:23:15.33,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,How's your leg doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.33,0:23:21.80,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Well, running and jumping are still a bit difficult for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.80,0:23:25.50,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,But I can walk normally now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.50,0:23:27.61,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,That's good to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.61,0:23:31.28,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,For now, make sure to rest properly, and then we'll start fresh again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.28,0:23:34.28,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Yes...!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.28,0:23:37.44,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...But still,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.44,0:23:40.82,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,It's hard not being able to do anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.82,0:23:46.66,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,While I'm just sitting here, everyone else is working hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.66,0:23:49.90,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,...Katsuragi-san, could you take a look at this for a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.90,0:23:53.00,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.00,0:23:56.83,Default,フォロワー,0,0,0,,Is it true you got injured? Please take it easy and rest up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.83,0:24:01.44,Default,フォロワー,0,0,0,,I love seeing you work hard, Katsuragi-san. But please be careful not to overdo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.44,0:24:05.68,Default,フォロワー,0,0,0,,Please take it easy for now. Once you're better, show us your energetic self again.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.68,0:24:08.48,Default,フォロワー,0,0,0,,We love you! We'll be waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.48,0:24:12.48,Default,フォロワー,0,0,0,,We're always cheering for you. Please take care of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.48,0:24:14.55,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.55,0:24:17.96,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,These are words of encouragement from your fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.96,0:24:21.66,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Are these from my fans...?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.66,0:24:25.33,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,That's right. Everyone is eagerly waiting for your comeback, Katsuragi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.33,0:24:28.87,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,They're looking forward to the day they can see you again, Katsuragi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.55,0:24:32.97,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.97,0:24:39.83,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,To have them support someone like me...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.83,0:24:41.08,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.08,0:24:45.95,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Once you get better, get back on stage, and express your gratitude to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.32,0:24:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,One week later.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.19,0:24:54.63,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Katsuragi-san, are you all set and ready to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.63,0:24:56.40,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Yes...!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.40,0:24:59.06,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Just to be safe, how's your ankle doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.06,0:25:01.13,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'm all set...!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.13,0:25:03.77,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Then there's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.77,0:25:07.54,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Please give your fans a good show.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.54,0:25:09.37,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Yes...!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.37,0:25:12.78,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'm giving it everything I've got right now...!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.61,0:25:15.41,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Senpai...!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.41,0:25:17.92,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I... I did it...!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.92,0:25:21.79,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Congratulations on passing! That was an amazing performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.79,0:25:24.35,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.35,0:25:28.63,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I feel like I was able to perform beyond my usual self...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.63,0:25:31.63,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'm sure... it's thanks to all the fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.63,0:25:33.90,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,It's all thanks to the support I received.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.90,0:25:36.17,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...And of course, you too, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.17,0:25:40.41,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,You really know how to turn your fans' support into your own strength, don't you, Katsuragi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.41,0:25:42.30,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.30,0:25:46.41,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Today, I really felt like everyone gave me their strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.41,0:25:49.38,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,But we can't just sit back and celebrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.38,0:25:53.12,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Now that you've passed the audition, the next step is the live performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.12,0:25:56.14,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.14,0:26:00.16,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'm starting to feel nervous about the performance...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.16,0:26:03.96,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,You were able to show your strength during the special audition, so you'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.96,0:26:08.10,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Since you've gained strength from your fans' support, make sure to express your gratitude to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.94,0:26:13.30,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...My gratitude...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.30,0:26:17.68,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,The people who supported you, are waiting, Katsuragi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.68,0:26:19.51,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.51,0:26:24.92,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'll give everyone the best performance I can right now...!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.92,0:26:28.62,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Yes, because that's the greatest way to repay your fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.62,0:26:30.64,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'll do my best...!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.64,0:26:33.86,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.26,0:26:40.40,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Katsuragi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.40,0:26:43.04,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Oh, Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.04,0:26:45.50,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.50,0:26:47.64,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,That was an amazing performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.64,0:26:51.60,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'm really... exhausted, but
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.60,0:26:52.98,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I gave it my all.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.98,0:26:55.50,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,After the show ended,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.50,0:26:59.02,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I thanked everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.02,0:27:02.59,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I told them, "Thanks for cheering me on."
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.59,0:27:08.46,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Then, even more thank-yous came pouring in...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.46,0:27:09.89,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I was surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.89,0:27:13.63,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,They did that because of your performance, Katsuragi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.63,0:27:17.04,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Hehe, I'm so glad...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.04,0:27:20.71,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,Oh, you're still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.71,0:27:23.61,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Oh, from back then...!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.61,0:27:25.81,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,(Is that a Gokugetsu Academy uniform...?)
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.81,0:27:28.91,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,I can't believe you haven't given up yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.91,0:27:31.91,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,Clinging to something so pathetic...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.91,0:27:35.19,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...Because being stubborn is my best trait.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.19,0:27:37.25,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,Those eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.25,0:27:39.56,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,I still don't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.56,0:27:43.10,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,Where does that confidence even come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.10,0:27:46.30,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,Seriously, from just that kind of performance?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.30,0:27:51.84,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,This confidence was given to me by Senpai and all my friends
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.84,0:27:55.21,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,You don't get it, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.21,0:27:58.48,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,All that effort is pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.48,0:28:01.88,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,It's not pointless at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.88,0:28:04.06,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.06,0:28:07.06,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,I find that hard to believe...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.06,0:28:10.89,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,Do you really think that if you don't give up, your dreams will come true?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.89,0:28:14.36,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,It's not that I necessarily believe it will come true...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.36,0:28:17.96,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,Then why do you think it's not pointless?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.96,0:28:22.77,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Because I've decided to keep running until my dreams come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.77,0:28:24.50,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Katsuragi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.50,0:28:27.92,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,...It makes my skin crawl.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.92,0:28:31.48,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,All your fairytale lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.48,0:28:34.68,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I won't hesitate anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.68,0:28:38.88,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I won't be swayed by your words anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.88,0:28:41.95,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,...you're just stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.95,0:28:45.09,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,You don't have a shred of talent as an idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.09,0:28:47.55,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,Hey, Producer.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.55,0:28:50.69,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,Why did you choose {\i1}this{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.69,0:28:54.23,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,You really have no eye for talent, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.33,0:28:59.34,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,It's alright, Katsuragi-san. Didn't I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.11,0:29:03.39,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,As long as we can smile in the end, that's all that matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.04,0:29:08.85,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.85,0:29:13.65,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'll become a top idol!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.65,0:29:15.92,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,What are you suddenly talking about...?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.92,0:29:18.82,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,No matter how many years it takes,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.82,0:29:22.63,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Someday... I'll become a top idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.63,0:29:23.93,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'll prove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.93,0:29:29.47,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,The idol that Senpai chose can truly shine!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.47,0:29:32.22,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,...This girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.22,0:29:35.91,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,That being the case, please leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.91,0:29:37.45,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,Hmph...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.45,0:29:39.75,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,I understand perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.75,0:29:43.61,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,Neither of you have any talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.61,0:29:46.95,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,I won't tolerate any more insults towards Katsuragi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.95,0:29:48.83,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,Insults?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.83,0:29:51.55,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,It's just a fact...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.55,0:29:53.56,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,Fine, have it your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.56,0:29:55.63,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,Next time we meet,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.63,0:29:59.58,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,I'll show you how reality really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.77,0:30:03.87,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,She's finally gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.87,0:30:05.87,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.87,0:30:08.44,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Um, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.44,0:30:12.61,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Are we participating in 'FINALE' next?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.61,0:30:16.11,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm sure she'll be there too.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.11,0:30:19.12,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,First-year student at Gokugetsu Academy, Shion Shirakusa.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.12,0:30:22.79,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Regardless of her true nature, her talent and popularity are the real deal. She's a formidable opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.79,0:30:24.86,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.86,0:30:29.79,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I don't want to lose to someone who's always looking down on others.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.60,0:30:34.16,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Katsuragi-san, the audition we're participating in is—
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.16,0:30:36.20,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,"FINALE."
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.20,0:30:37.95,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,That person—
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.95,0:30:41.17,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Shirakusa-san is participating too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.17,0:30:44.57,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,It seems so. She's rumored to be the favorite this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.57,0:30:50.18,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...Actually, I watched a video of Shirakusa-san's live performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.18,0:30:52.15,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,She was really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.15,0:30:54.57,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Both her singing and dancing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.57,0:30:57.15,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,She's far beyond someone like me...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.15,0:31:01.02,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...I really don't like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.06,0:31:05.56,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,But I do respect her skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.56,0:31:10.27,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I think my chances of winning are quite low.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.27,0:31:12.64,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,But still, that doesn't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.64,0:31:15.81,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,That doesn't mean we should give up, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.81,0:31:17.51,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Yes...!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.51,0:31:20.54,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Katsuragi-san, just do what you always do.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.54,0:31:23.95,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Can I really win by just being myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.95,0:31:26.28,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,It's true, Shirakusa-san is a formidable opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.28,0:31:29.82,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Still, there are areas where you're better.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.82,0:31:32.76,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Really...?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.76,0:31:36.96,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,You understand your weaknesses. You know where you fall short.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.96,0:31:40.83,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,That's why you work harder than anyone else. Sometimes, you even overdo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.83,0:31:46.37,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Is that the one thing where I'm better than her...?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.37,0:31:47.81,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.81,0:31:52.08,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Katsuragi-san's "normal" is anything but ordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.24,0:31:57.48,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,I've come to realize something again. You're weak. And that's precisely why you're stronger than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.92,0:32:01.89,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.63,0:32:06.32,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'm starting to feel a little more confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.32,0:32:09.46,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'll do my very best...!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.60,0:32:12.43,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Katsuragi-san, you won.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.43,0:32:13.66,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...What?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.66,0:32:15.93,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I... won...?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.93,0:32:18.14,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Yes. Is it hard to believe?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.14,0:32:21.77,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,You beat Shirakusa-san and won the whole thing, Katsuragi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.46,0:32:25.73,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Um, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.73,0:32:29.25,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Of course, I intended to win, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.25,0:32:32.02,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Why... was I able to win?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.02,0:32:33.89,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Well, that's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.89,0:32:35.79,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,It was just a fluke.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.79,0:32:37.49,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,...Shirakusa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.49,0:32:40.63,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,No... it wasn't even a fluke.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.63,0:32:43.36,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,The judges were just blind to the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.36,0:32:46.50,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,It's obvious that I'm the more talented one.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.50,0:32:49.50,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,I refuse to accept this result...!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.50,0:32:52.07,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Your voice is shaking, Shirakusa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.07,0:32:54.21,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,W-What are you...!?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.21,0:33:00.14,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...It's true, I do think my skills are inferior to yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.14,0:33:03.11,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.11,0:33:06.12,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,Then why don't you just withdraw right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.12,0:33:08.19,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,If you do that, then—
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.19,0:33:11.92,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,—But in the end, I was the one who won.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.92,0:33:15.36,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Y-you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.36,0:33:19.54,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...So, please take back what you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.54,0:33:22.43,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,What you said about Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.04,0:33:29.90,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,I'm not wrong...!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.90,0:33:32.90,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,You guys don't have any talent!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.16,0:33:37.08,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...Why do you have to go that far?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.08,0:33:41.28,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,It's alright, Katsuragi-san. There's no need for her to take back what she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.28,0:33:43.82,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,You've already proved yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.82,0:33:45.66,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,...You!!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.66,0:33:47.49,Default,アイドルA,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, what's that all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.49,0:33:51.03,Default,アイドルB,0,0,0,,Is there some kind of argument? Didn't one of them pass?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.66,0:33:57.13,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,I will never forgive those incompetents.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.13,0:34:01.43,Default,白草四音,0,0,0,,I will definitely clear this humiliation...!!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.34,0:34:07.68,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,She doesn't trust anyone. She just has the skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.68,0:34:12.02,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,I don't believe a performance from someone who doesn't open their heart can truly reach anyone else's.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.02,0:34:18.36,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...Did my performance really reach their hearts?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.36,0:34:22.32,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Even you believed in Shirakusa-san. You thought, "That girl is strong."
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.32,0:34:26.70,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,That's why you kept working so hard. You always gave it her all.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.70,0:34:30.53,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.53,0:34:35.74,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Because that's a given.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.74,0:34:45.62,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,If I don't recognize the strength of others, and my own weaknesses, I can't even get to the starting line.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.62,0:34:48.32,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,That's what makes you so appealing, Katsuragi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.32,0:34:52.59,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Even if your skills were rough, your performance must have moved the judges.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.63,0:34:57.33,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.33,0:34:59.73,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,You know, it's okay to be happier about this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.73,0:35:03.49,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...Even though I'm the one who passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.49,0:35:07.44,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,It's true that I'm not as skilled yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.44,0:35:11.74,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...So, the next time we meet,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.74,0:35:14.98,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'll become strong enough to win on my own merits...!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.98,0:35:17.38,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,...That's just like you, Katsuragi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.61,0:37:02.40,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.40,0:37:05.56,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Did you watch me?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.56,0:37:07.66,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Of course, I was watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.66,0:37:11.43,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Did I do okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.43,0:37:14.40,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Yes. It was an amazing performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.91,0:37:19.59,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Well, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.59,0:37:24.94,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I was so focused that I don't really remember much about the performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.94,0:37:28.44,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...Before I knew it, I was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.44,0:37:30.48,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,You really gave it your all.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.42,0:37:33.79,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.40,0:37:37.15,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I think I really gave it my all.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.15,0:37:43.09,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,All I remember was how much fun it was, and one more thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.09,0:37:46.20,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,...the expressions on the faces of the people who came to the venue.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.20,0:37:51.68,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Before it started, I was nervous and anxious...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.47,0:37:55.14,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I had a stomachache, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.14,0:37:57.34,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Standing on stage,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.72,0:38:02.78,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Seeing everyone's faces helped me calm down a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.78,0:38:04.62,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,...Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.62,0:38:06.88,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I realized something.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.88,0:38:12.86,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,The people here were cheering for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.86,0:38:16.50,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,If I couldn't live up to those expectations...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.50,0:38:22.00,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Then I couldn't become the idol I admired back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.00,0:38:23.97,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,That's what I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.97,0:38:27.31,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,After that, I was just desperate to give it my all.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.31,0:38:31.04,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,On stage, you were already a remarkable idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.04,0:38:35.28,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.28,0:38:39.34,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Senpai, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.34,0:38:42.19,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'll become a top idol!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.19,0:38:44.99,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'll keep giving it my all!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.99,0:38:48.39,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,That's the spirit. Would you like to review the video of the performance?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.39,0:38:49.76,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Oh...!?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.76,0:38:52.66,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,I'd love to see it...!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.66,0:38:56.30,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Would you join me for a review session?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.30,0:38:58.57,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Of course, I'll join you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.14,0:39:01.80,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.80,0:39:05.75,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,From now on, and forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.75,0:39:08.71,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Until the day I can smile at the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.71,0:39:11.87,Default,葛城リーリヤ,0,0,0,,Thank you so much, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.50,0:42:00.54,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Let's reflect on today's production.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.54,0:42:04.19,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Katsuragi-san never stopped moving forward. That's why she soared so high this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.19,0:42:08.13,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,However, there's a certain risk in her progress. ...It's my fault that she stumbled.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.13,0:42:12.06,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,It's my job to guide her. I told her to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.06,0:42:16.03,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,Words carry responsibility. I, too, must prove myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.03,0:42:20.17,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,To be a producer worthy of a future top idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.17,0:42:23.21,Default,プロデューサー,0,0,0,,The next step is... 'H.I.F.'.
